    feat: add Health Map + Problems panels to Dev tab command center
    
    Health Map panel:
      - Color-coded grid of all 15 components (green/yellow/orange/red)
      - Click any component to drill down into its timeline
      - Timeline shows Genesis key events, activity gaps, errors
      - Dependency graph shows upstream/downstream components
      - Auto-remediation actions displayed with status
      - Configurable time window (15min / 1hr / 6hr / 24hr)
    
    Problems panel:
      - All current problems listed with severity color
      - Critical vs degrading counts
      - Error rates, event counts, last-seen timestamps
      - Pending approval queue with approve/reject buttons
      - Scan & Heal button for immediate remediation
      - Remediation action log
    
    Co-authored-by: aaron031291 <aaron031291@users.noreply.github.com>
